It is assumed that id field is unique for Item.
It is assumed that currency of money is fixed as GBP for all Item. There is aCurrency field is put in Price bu assumed as fixed

Some payment classes are created but payment method and details are ignored.

There is a main method in Runner class if you want to run as java application.
There are detailed tests that you can run to see the flow of application.


Sample Output
[item:bread	quantity:1	Amount:10
, item:tea	quantity:3	Amount:60
, item:banana	quantity:5	Amount:25
]
Actual Total:95
Total Discount Amount:35
Vat Percentage:	20
